 4  ## Warning message codes:
 
 5  # terminals must have 1 in tens place, non-terminals with 2
 
 6  # additional types from 00-09 (models make use of this format)
 
 7  W_UNCERTVAL = 00 
 8  W_TERMEVENT = 10 
 9  W_TERMSTATEBD = 11 
10  W_BISECTLIMIT = 12 
11  W_NONTERMEVENT = 20 
12  W_NONTERMSTATEBD = 21 
13  
 
14  ## Error message codes
 
15  # computation errors have 0 in tens place, event errors have 1 in tens place
 
16  E_COMPUTFAIL    = 00 
17  E_NONUNIQUETERM = 10 
18

20                 E_COMPUTFAIL: 'Computation of trajectory failed'}
